snippet.title: The Complex Tragedy - Trailer
snippet.description:
The Complex Tragedy is a single-player horror game set in a massive living complex. While exploring different areas, you will feel the fear as you uncover the creepy and deserted side of the complex. Brace yourself for spine-chilling experience within The Complex.

Check out the Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2767400/The_Complex_Tragedy/
